個有諗頭，可不可以幫手spread出去，謝謝<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1）警察衰野太多，好難一張文宣講晒<br />\n2）我地前線手足都開始反擊得勁D，反擊畫面又會被現在好落力打國際戰的政府拎黎大造文章，條片正好俾外國能更好地體諒我地<br />\n3）更好利用一些震撼畫面或者橋段，收籠外國人心<br />\n4）微電影，睇故仔，好多人都會幾OK，有助spread我地情況出去<br />\n5）以後我地本地同外國文宣都塞條片的link入去，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到，sosaad。"},{"pid":"4c759e7bb755cfb8063ba3ad477d7d920320e480","tid":1572044,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"大約幾時會call<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cc2d85f3d415a8b7b37ae90b0ea1df5f232918","tid":1572044,"uid":14880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T15:28:02.000Z","msg":"Sd 左幾次cv都無回聲 in都既得in<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fd16a1431377727c7c7344734a6909ec2b79ad","tid":1572044,"uid":14880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08cc2d85f3d415a8b7b37ae90b0ea1df5f232918","tid":1572044,"uid":14880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T15:28:02.000Z","msg":"Sd 左幾次cv都無回聲 in都既得in<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"回音 in都無得in*"},{"pid":"51daa3385b238d468520a08edab0db4450bf2bce","tid":1572044,"uid":74417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c759e7bb755cfb8063ba3ad477d7d920320e480","tid":1572044,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"大約幾時會call<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"我都等緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm